  targetNames:
  - There's no time for a soak! Destroy all houses with <color="orange">bathtubs</color>
    - those bubbles won't pop themselves!
  - 'Mission: Wipe the <color="orange">traffic cones</color>! They stole them from
    us! I want to see a cone-tastic clean city!'
  - QUACK! We have to tear down every owner with a <color="orange">rubber duck</color>!
    That was not my idea, blame the developer!
  - The trash talk is over. Take out the <color="orange">rubbish bins</color> ...
    and the houses with them!
  - Water you waiting for? Time to drain the competition by taking down every house
    with a <color="orange">water barrel</color>!
  targetShadowNames:
  - There's no time for a soak! Destroy all houses with <color="black">bathtubs</color>
    - those bubbles won't pop themselves!
  - 'Mission: Wipe the <color="black">traffic cones</color>! They stole them from
    us! I want to see a cone-tastic clean city!'
  - QUACK! We have to tear down every owner with a <color="black">rubber duck</color>!
